<br>
<br>
Get puppet strings from PoF, 10 charges of allure.<br>
<br>
Get ench and shaman and bard to debuff the Forman and right click strings until charm lands, quickly hand in two jades and you get a sledgemallet<br>
<br>
<br>
As for captain and braids, try this:<br>
<br>
Get someone to pull him to a zone, then mez him, put braids in trade window and have a grouped casters invis you, then click hand it.<br>
<br>
-Daegs<br>
PS i'm not sure how Mez affects trade windows, so not sure if that would work, but i know the charming works for sledgemallet.<br>
<br>
