<font color="blue">Ahura Myndbender 55 Enchanter</font><br> <img src="http://www.talthalra.com/tenpic.jpg" width="213" height="215"></font></font></font></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udrakinn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drakinn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 11:05:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23186.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dont know if Capt Rottgrime is charmable or not- but,</span><hr size=1> well, if you can get invis while in the trade window, you could wait until mez wore off and THEN click transfer, as long as the capt doesnt see invis <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umelodiesongbird.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Melodie Songbird</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/6/02 1:23:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23186.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dont know if Capt Rottgrime is charmable or not- but,</span><hr size=1> You could always kill that one mob in MM that gives +VS faction for a while too.  Advisor I think?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usquinkmcpoke.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Squink McPoke</A></span><br> <